  <brief_title>Postoperative Nausea and Vomiting: to Estimate the Incidence and Risk Factors in a Tertiary Teaching Hospital</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postoperative Nausea and Vomiting: A Prospective Observational Study to Estimate the Incidence and Risk Factors Over One Year in a Tertiary Teaching Hospital</official_title>
